## Amenities

Our state-of-the-art amenities are created to complement your new lifestyle at the Hills, and they include, but not limited to; community center with retail shops and services, 24-hour security, kids play areas, spacious green areas with water features, jogging tracks, and a dedicated multi-purpose building hall for various occasions and functions such as weddings, international conferences, and events.

